      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.314013195
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……だ、大丈夫？\n全身ボロボロじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.1948782285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "あの電流と爆破、見た目が派手なだけで\n人体に害はないって話らしいけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.4271229744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫なんだぜぇ……\n俺様は特別、頑丈だからなぁ……ひ～、は～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5610322878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "ひーはーに覇気がなくなってるじゃない\nでも、大丈夫なら良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6910228767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.0872139295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "改めて、楽しいバトルだったわ\nあなたのパフォーマンスも、凄く良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.5934950829
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "ラップは淀みないしロックな歌詞も熱くて\n聴き応えがあった。歌、うまいのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.1333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.1568736713
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ。私達のパフォーマンスはどうだった？\n対戦相手として、いちファンとして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "へへ……自分のパフォーマンスに精一杯でよぉ\nあんたらを観てる余裕なんてなかったぜぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.283268261
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "あら、そうだったの？\nもったいないわね、せっかく私のファンなのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.0510688465
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ。それなら逆に\nここで負けてラッキーかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.7904566129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "だって次のバトルからは\nいち観客としてじっくり見れるでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.9629961014
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "ほら立って。そして、観てて\n最高のパフォーマンスで、元気づけてあげるからっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1666664124,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4958.63548909999,
          "startTime": 117.1253019015
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5342.942468699988,
          "startTime": 117.5096088811
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.8753019015
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "リングアナウンサー鈴木",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-suzukiana002.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ続いてのバトルはぁ……！\nレイレイ、メイメイ、アオアオの登場だぁ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.6333330791,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9133.332570300012,
          "startTime": 129.7666656494
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9517.639549899997,
          "startTime": 130.150972629
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "みんなー！　盛り上がってるー！？\nまだまだ声出せるでしょう！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4104545024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの、アイドルを好きって気持ち\nもっともっと滾らせて！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5999895732,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9433.3437601,
          "startTime": 143.0333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9817.650739700013,
          "startTime": 143.4176403129
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "ここにいる全員で、最高のステージを作りましょう！\nさあ、ぶち上げていくわよー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8999875386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（最初はアングラな大会だから、なんて思ったけど）\n（場所も舞台も、怜には関係ないんだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.9333147684,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7299.997202399993,
          "startTime": 156.2333119708
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7684.304181999977,
          "startTime": 156.6176189504
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（いつどんな時も変わらず会場を盛り上げて）\n（輝く怜は……最高のエンターテイナーだよ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.3666450499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "その熱気、最高よ！\nメイメイ、アオアオ、準備はいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.2333117166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "最高のパフォーマンスを見せつけてやろう！\n――『COMETIC DANCER』！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.8663163295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.5654239651,
      "sfxList": [
