      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、だ、大丈夫ですか？\nそんな、コーヒー吹き出して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.5332903542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、野良アイドルを探してるんです\n詳しいことは、その、言えないんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.7666236875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
