      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "この前、芽衣と葵とで\nイベントへ遊びに行ったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.3999570208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "そこで、世紀末パンクラップアイドル\nまきびし丸withスズキって人達に出会ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.1999570208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "結構いいパフォーマンスをしていたので\n勉強も兼ねてライブを観に行きたいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.7332903542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "周りのスタッフさんとか、あの雫でさえ\n聞いたこともないアイドルだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.2659367656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（そりゃあ、俺と鈴木さんとで組んだ）\n（あの日限りの即席グループだからな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.6054963579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "それに、その……イベントの時\nまきびし丸さんとは少しだけ話が出来たんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.5332903542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei027.m4a",
      "text": "冷静に考えると、ちょっと赤裸々に\n話し過ぎちゃったなって。素性も分からない人なのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.7915718232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei028.m4a",
      "text": "だから、出来れば口止めしておきたくて\n知らないところで広まっちゃうのは、嫌ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.9332903542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（そんな変な話だったかな？　まきびし丸を演じるのに）\n（一杯一杯で、俺が忘れてる……とか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.5666236875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみになんだけど\nどんな話をしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.8332903542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei029.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ！？　い……今はまだ、内緒です\n特に、{user}さんには",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.8332903542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei030.m4a",
      "text": "今はまだ、その……\n話せるタイミングじゃないっていうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.8332903542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei031.m4a",
      "text": "だから、その時が来るまでは\n私をマネジメントしながら、気長に待ってて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.5332903542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_16_03-rei032.m4a",
      "text": "いつか、伝えてもいいかなって思えるようになったら\nちゃんと{user}さんにも教えますから",
      "translations": {
